text: Nikolina Zadravec (born 2 September 1997) is a Croatian handball player for RK Podravka and the Croatian national team.EHF profile She participated at the 2016 European Women's Handball Championship.2016 European Championship roster ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian female handball players Category:Sportspeople from Čakovec
